(18425, 'Epilog 250mg/5ml 10 amp. for i.v. inj.', 'ابيلوج 250 مجم / 5 مل 10 امبول', '30', '50', 'Phenytoin', 'Mup', 'Inj', 'حقن', 'يستخدم في علاج الصرع حيث يعمل العلاج على إبطاء السيالات العصبية و منع تكون نوبات الصرع أو السيطرة عليها', 'Anti-epileptic.hydantoin', '250mg', 'Phenytoin is indicated to treat grand mal seizures, complex partial seizures, and to prevent and treat seizures during or following neurosurgery.[L9362] Injectable phenytoin and [Fosphenytoin], which is the phosphate ester prodrug formulation of phenytoin[A188571], are indicated to treat tonic-clonic status epilepticus, and for the prevention and treatment of seizures occurring during neurosurgery.[L10740]', '', '', 1708, '2024-12-19', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
